act:
1716959 THE NATIONAL CO- OPERATIVE DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION ACT, 1962
ACT NO. 26 OF 1962 [ 31st August, 1962.]
1 An Act to provide for the incorporation and regulation of a corporation for the purpose of planning and promoting programmes for the production, processing, marketing, storage, export and import of agricultural produce, foodstuffs and certain other commodities on co- operative principles and for matters connected therewith.]
411269 1 Short title, extent and commencement.
3762 1This Act may be called the National Co- operative Development Corporation Act, 1962.
1476351 2It extends to the whole of India 2
284797 3It shall come into force on such date 3 as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, appoint.
735508 2 Definitions. In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires,--
1231505 a" agricultural produce" 4 includes the following] classes of commodities, namely:--
1998856 i5 edible oil- seeds;
851693 iicattle fodder, including oil- cakes and other concentrates;
431659 iiiraw cotton, whether ginned or unginned and cotton seed;
602591 ivraw jute; and
