1519464 3 Establishment of the National Co- operative Development Corporation.
854337 1The Central Government shall, by notification in the Official Gazette, establish with effect from such date 3 as may be specified in the notification, a Corporation by the name of the National Co- operative Development Corporation which shall be a body corporate having perpetual succession and a common seal with power to acquire, hold and dispose of property and to contract, and may, in the said name, sue and be sued.
1720774 2The head- office of the Corporation shall be in New Delhi.
1508197 34 The Corporation shall carry on its functions through the General Council and the Board. 80 1Ins. by Act 3 of 1974, s. 3 (w. e. f. 1- 4- 1974). 2 Ins. by Act 32 of 1973, s. 3. 3 14th March, 1963, vide Notification No. G. S. R. 457, dated 14- 3- 1963, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Pt. II, Sec. 3 (i), p. 149. 4 Subs. by Act 3 of 1974, s. 4, for the former sub- sections (3), (4) and (5) (w. e. f. 7- 4- 1975).
159182 4The General Council shall consist of the following members, namely:--
1946943 ia President and a Vice- President, both to be nominated by the Central Government;
817776 iieight members, ex officio, to be nominated by the Central Government from such of its Ministries dealing with economic matters as it may think fit;
517015 iiiDeputy Governor of the Reserve Bank in charge of rural credit, ex officio;
1943500 ivManaging Director of the State Bank, ex officio;
